OL,3,CRwanda asylum scheme cost could soar
OL,4,Cto #500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThe cost of Rishi Sunak's troubled
OL,7,FRwanda asylum scheme could soar to
OL,8,Fhalf a billion pounds, plus hundreds
OL,9,Fof thousands more for each deportee,
OL,10,Fan investigation by the public
OL,11,Fspending watchdog has found.
OL,13,FThe Home Office has so far refused to
OL,14,Fsay how much more money, on top of the
OL,15,F#290 million already confirmed, the UK
OL,16,Fhas agreed to pay Kigali under the
OL,17,Fstalled plan, but a National Audit
OL,18,FOffice report has revealed millions
OL,19,Fmore in spending including #11,000 for
OL,20,Feach migrant's plane ticket.
