OL,3,CRwanda asylum scheme cost could soar
OL,4,Cto #500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FCritics said the "staggering figures"
OL,7,Freveal "the extortionate bill the
OL,8,Ftaxpayer will have to pay the Rwandan
OL,9,Fgovernment for an unworkable and
OL,10,Finhumane scheme" and "the national
OL,11,Fscandal the Tories have been trying to
OL,12,Fhide".
OL,14,FThe Government has already paid Kigali
OL,15,F#220 million under the Economic
OL,16,FTransformation and Integration Fund
OL,17,Fdesigned to support Rwanda's growth,
OL,18,Feven as flights have remained grounded
OL,19,Famid a series of legal setbacks.
