OL,6,FIn addition, an extra #20,000 will be
OL,7,Fpaid to Rwanda for every asylum seeker
OL,8,Frelocated there, according to the NAO
OL,9,Freport.
OL,11,FThe Home Office will also separately
OL,12,Fhand Kigali nearly #151,000 per person
OL,13,Fto cover asylum processing and
OL,14,Fintegration costs, such as
OL,15,Faccommodation, food, healthcare and
OL,16,Feducation, over five years if they
OL,17,Fstay in the country.
