OL,3,CRwanda asylum scheme cost could soar
OL,4,Cto #500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FNo asylum seeker who has arrived in
OL,7,Fthe UK via unauthorised means has so
OL,8,Ffar been removed to Rwanda under the
OL,9,FConservatives' flagship asylum policy,
OL,10,Falthough the Prime Minister has said
OL,11,Fhe wants flights to start "as soon as
OL,12,Fpractically possible".
OL,14,FThe Home Office has also already
OL,15,Fincurred direct costs of #20 million
OL,16,Fin establishing the agreement,
OL,17,Fincluding set-up charges for escorting
OL,18,Fmigrants on the one-way trip and
OL,19,Ftraining facilities, legal fees and
OL,20,Fstaff.
