OL,3,CRwanda asylum scheme cost could soar
OL,4,Cto #500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FThis is expected to rise to #28
OL,7,Fmillion by the end of the year,
OL,8,Faccording to the watchdog.
OL,10,FThe department estimates that future
OL,11,Fcosts will include #11,000 per asylum
OL,12,Fseeker for flights to Rwanda, covering
OL,13,Fthe charter of non-commercial planes
OL,14,Fand fuel, the NAO said.
OL,16,FSome #12.6 million will also be spent
OL,17,Fon training people to escort migrants
OL,18,Fin the first year and #1 million per
OL,19,Fyear thereafter, and #1 million
OL,20,Fannually in staff costs.
