OL,6,FThe Rwanda policy is a key plank of Mr
OL,7,FSunak's plan to "stop the boats", as
OL,8,Fhe believes it will be a deterrent to
OL,9,Ffurther Channel crossings.
OL,11,FNo migrants have so far been removed
OL,12,Fbecause of the legal challenges that
OL,13,Fresulted in the Supreme Court finding
OL,14,Fthe scheme unlawful.
