OL,6,FMr Sunak is trying to revive the
OL,7,Fpolicy by passing legislation deeming
OL,8,FRwanda a safe country and ratifying a
OL,9,Fnew treaty with Kigali. The Rwanda
OL,10,FBill is currently making its way
OL,11,Fthrough a House of Lords that is
OL,12,Fhostile to the scheme.
OL,14,FLabour's shadow home secretary Yvette
OL,15,FCooper said: "This report reveals the
OL,16,Fnational scandal the Tories have been
OL,17,Ftrying to hide. Its shocking analysis
OL,18,Fshows the costs of the failed Rwanda
OL,19,Ffarce are even higher than previously
OL,20,Fthought.
