OL,4,Cto #500m, watchdog says
OL,6,F"In order to send less than 1% of UK
OL,7,Fasylum seekers to Rwanda on a few
OL,8,Fsymbolic flights, the taxpayer will be
OL,9,Fforced to fork out over half a billion
OL,10,Fpounds ` with no ability to recover
OL,11,Fany of the money already sent. This is
OL,12,Fthe equivalent of nearly #2 million
OL,13,Fper person sent.
OL,15,F"Rishi Sunak has staked his position
OL,16,Fon this scheme. He must account for
OL,17,Fthis fiasco."
