OL,4,Cto #500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FHome Affairs Committee chairwoman Dame
OL,7,FDiana Johnson said: "These are
OL,8,Fstaggering figures. For all its
OL,9,Frhetoric about ensuring value for
OL,10,Fmoney in the asylum and immigration
OL,11,Fsystem it is unclear how schemes such
OL,12,Fas Rwanda or Bibby Stockholm achieve
OL,13,Fthat. Huge initial outlay and ongoing
OL,14,Fcosts raise serious questions about
OL,15,Fhow this can be cost effective, even
OL,16,Fcompared to high hotel accommodation
OL,17,Fcosts.
