OL,4,Cto #500m, watchdog says
OL,6,F"What we are left with is a very
OL,7,Fexpensive programme the Government
OL,8,Fhopes may offer a deterrent to those
OL,9,Fseeking to cross the Channel in small
OL,10,Fboats. Yet, there is little evidence
OL,11,Ffor this either...
OL,13,F"This also does little to allay the
OL,14,Fserious concerns ... about the lack of
OL,15,Fopenness on the cost implications of
OL,16,Fthe Rwanda scheme from the Home
OL,17,FOffice. For a scheme whose importance
OL,18,Fis apparently self-evident, we would
OL,19,Fexpect the evidence base to be far
OL,20,Fclearer, not presented in dribs and
OL,21,Fdrabs and getting worse every time."
